{"tha-ap309:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap309:0.2":"Padumakesaravagga ","tha-ap309:0.3":"Aramadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap309:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap309:1.2":"aramo ropito maya; ","tha-ap309:1.3":"Sandacchayesu rukkhesu, ","tha-ap309:1.4":"upasantesu pakkhisu. ","tha-ap309:2.1":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap309:2.2":"ahutinam patiggaham; ","tha-ap309:2.3":"Aramam abhinamesim, ","tha-ap309:2.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap309:3.1":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap309:3.2":"phalam pupphamadasaham; ","tha-ap309:3.3":"Tato jatappasadova, ","tha-ap309:3.4":"tam vanam parinamayim. ","tha-ap309:4.1":"Buddhassa yamidam dasim, ","tha-ap309:4.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap309:4.3":"Bhave nibbattamanamhi, ","tha-ap309:4.4":"nibbattati phalam mama. ","tha-ap309:5.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap309:5.2":"yam aramamadam tada; ","tha-ap309:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap309:5.4":"aramassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap309:6.1":"Sattatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap309:6.2":"sattasum mudusitala; ","tha-ap309:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap309:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap309:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap309:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap309:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap309:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma aramadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap309:9.1":"Aramadayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}